  "contentHtml": "<!-- BEGIN COPYRIGHTED TEXT CHUNK --><html><head></head><body><p><a id=\"passage-13\"><b>Heraññakani</b> (Thag 2.13) <span class=\"altID\">{Thag 145-146}</span></a>&nbsp;<a title=\"Go to top of page\" class=\"back\" href=\"#top\">&nbsp;</a></p>\n\n<div class=\"chapter\">\n\n<div class=\"freeverse\">\nDays &amp; nights\n\t   fly past.\nLife\n\tcomes to an end.\nThe span of mortals\n\t   runs out,\nlike the water of a piddling stream.\nBut the fool doing evil deeds\ndoesn't realize that later\nit's bitter for him:\nevil for him\n\t   the result.\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n</body></html>",
  "summary": "The results of evil deeds will catch up with you.",
